	    </listitem>
	  </VarListEntry>
	  <VarListEntry>
	    <Term><replaceable>drawable</replaceable>.<parameter>is_indexed</parameter></Term>
	    <ListItem>
	      <Para>Non zero if the drawable uses an indexed colour
